WEBVTT

00:00.007 --> 00:01.849
<i>Previously on Being Mary Jane...</i>

00:01.851 --> 00:05.395
They're trying to push me out,
and they are going to use you to do it.

00:05.397 --> 00:06.434
Cheers to that.

00:06.436 --> 00:08.297
And David--do you
know what I would give

00:08.299 --> 00:09.979
to have a man look at me
like that?

00:09.989 --> 00:11.687
Do yourself a favor;
get yourself some help,

00:11.689 --> 00:13.142
because I'm done.

00:13.144 --> 00:16.145
Being a baby mama
is not a career!

00:16.155 --> 00:18.929
You have no job, no skills,
and two mouths to feed!

00:18.931 --> 00:21.229
I just figured we'd have
a nice meal and some nice wine.

00:21.239 --> 00:24.047
It's just coming across corny.

00:24.172 --> 00:26.479
Before you say anything, I just
want to apologize for showing up.

00:26.489 --> 00:27.802
I'll call you tomorrow.

