04:53.847 --> 04:55.879
♪ ♪

04:55.889 --> 05:00.087
♪ Yes, heaven ♪

05:00.097 --> 05:02.546
♪ I'm in heaven ♪

05:02.556 --> 05:04.170
♪ ♪

05:04.180 --> 05:07.296
♪ And the cares
that hung around me ♪

05:07.306 --> 05:10.629
♪ Through the week ♪

05:10.639 --> 05:17.212
♪ Seems to vanish like
a gambler's lucky streak ♪

05:17.222 --> 05:19.379
♪ ♪

05:19.389 --> 05:24.920
♪ When we're out together,
dancing cheek to cheek ♪

05:24.930 --> 05:26.753
Take it, Ella. Swing it.

