33:39.422 --> 33:41.162
No, you know, I'm
sorry to keep cutting you off,

33:41.172 --> 33:43.954
but I really don't want you
to apologize.

33:43.964 --> 33:47.383
You know, one of the things
I-I liked about you, actually,

33:47.385 --> 33:49.093
is that you are
refreshingly honest,

33:49.095 --> 33:52.170
so thank you for telling me
about yourself.

33:52.172 --> 33:55.454
I honestly don't regret a thing.

33:57.422 --> 33:58.829
I called to pull you in closer,

33:58.839 --> 34:00.954
and I feel like
you're drifting away.

34:00.964 --> 34:02.703
No, I'm just finding my legs

34:02.713 --> 34:07.037
and finally figuring out
what I do want.

34:07.047 --> 34:08.286
I don't know
if marriage and kids

34:08.297 --> 34:10.703
are in the cards for me,
but I do know

34:10.713 --> 34:13.036
that I want to wake up
next to somebody every day

34:13.047 --> 34:16.371
and see my toothbrush next
to theirs, at the very least.

34:16.380 --> 34:19.786
♪ I'm a black mermaid ♪

34:19.797 --> 34:21.703
♪ ♪

34:21.713 --> 34:25.371
♪ From the bottom of the sea ♪

34:25.380 --> 34:26.454
♪ ♪

34:26.464 --> 34:28.911
I got to go, Sheldon.

34:28.922 --> 34:31.995
♪ ♪

34:32.005 --> 34:35.496
Um, our relationship
started on a phone,

34:35.505 --> 34:38.411
and it ends here too.

34:38.422 --> 34:40.286
Yeah.

34:40.297 --> 34:42.329
♪ ♪

34:42.339 --> 34:44.120
Good-bye or see you later?

34:44.130 --> 34:48.286
♪ ♪

34:48.297 --> 34:49.870
Good-bye.

34:49.880 --> 34:53.411
♪ I'm here for you to love me ♪

34:53.422 --> 34:55.079
Take care of yourself.

34:55.089 --> 34:59.496
♪ I'll be here
for all the time ♪

34:59.506 --> 35:01.703
♪ ♪

35:01.713 --> 35:04.412
♪ And I will wait for you
to see me ♪

35:04.422 --> 35:06.995
♪ And to understand ♪

35:07.005 --> 35:12.454
♪ That a woman can restore
the soul of any broken man ♪

35:12.464 --> 35:15.454
♪ If you can look beyond
the waves and... ♪

35:15.464 --> 35:17.454
I can't believe
she doesn't like dogs.

35:18.922 --> 35:21.204
Lisa, my life hasn't been
my own in quite some time,

35:21.214 --> 35:23.037
so if she doesn't want dogs
around

35:23.047 --> 35:24.787
'cause the baby's coming,
well then...

35:24.797 --> 35:26.204
That may work for now,
but that's something

35:26.214 --> 35:29.496
you're gonna have to talk out
and figure out.

35:29.506 --> 35:31.954
Yeah. You know what?

35:31.964 --> 35:33.954
