don't talk anymore.

35:52.922 --> 35:56.037
Oh. I thought the two of you
were at least still cordial.

35:56.047 --> 35:58.412
Well...

35:58.422 --> 36:00.912
How you doing? You look good.

36:00.922 --> 36:02.079
I am.

36:02.089 --> 36:03.412
Your friend Valerie,

36:03.422 --> 36:06.204
