about the joke before.

36:14.713 --> 36:17.287
Please. I am figuring out
all my issues.

36:17.297 --> 36:18.870
Really?
- Mm-hmm.

36:18.880 --> 36:20.329
Figured out some triggers.

36:20.339 --> 36:21.454
That's really good, man.

36:21.464 --> 36:23.714
I was hoping that she'd be able--
- Yeah, you're one.

36:26.089 --> 36:28.954
Me?
- You.

36:28.964 --> 36:31.204
Why? How?

36:31.214 --> 36:32.287
Come on, David.

36:32.297 --> 36:33.287
Come on, what?

36:33.297 --> 36:35.037
Where are we going? What?

36:35.047 --> 36:38.246
Look, you've always known
