36:38.256 --> 36:39.787
Yeah, we're friends.

36:39.797 --> 36:41.079
Don't do that, David.

36:41.089 --> 36:42.703
Don't do what?

36:42.713 --> 36:45.287
Look, I know you don't share
the same feelings as me.

36:45.297 --> 36:48.079
I'm clear about that.

36:48.089 --> 36:51.496
I'm just ready to own the fact
that I carry feelings for you.

36:51.506 --> 36:54.037
I'm not proud of it.

36:54.047 --> 36:57.412
And, in fact, I have a lot
of guilt surrounding it,

36:57.422 --> 36:59.162
and I want to tell Mary Jane.

36:59.172 --> 37:01.703
Ugh, if I just--
I know she may never forgive me,

37:01.713 --> 37:03.703
but if I'm ever gonna have
a chance

37:03.713 --> 37:05.538
of regaining
my relationship with her,

37:05.548 --> 37:08.120
I need to begin again
in truth.

37:08.130 --> 37:09.829
Oh, my God.

37:09.839 --> 37:12.954
What is happening to me?

37:17.130 --> 37:19.079
Hey.

37:19.089 --> 37:20.787
What are you doing?

37:20.797 --> 37:24.162
Heading home.
- What are you doing?

37:24.172 --> 37:26.829
Negro, do not act like
me loving you is new for you.

37:26.839 --> 37:28.329
Well, then how
I am supposed to act?

37:28.339 --> 37:29.870
'Cause that's exactly
what this is.

37:29.880 --> 37:32.496
No, you cannot act
like I got here by myself.

37:32.506 --> 37:33.870
Lisa, look.

37:33.880 --> 37:36.496
I understand that that one night
meant a lot to you--

37:36.506 --> 37:38.912
That night and all the ones
that followed.

37:38.922 --> 37:40.745
Oral sex is still sex.

37:40.755 --> 37:43.538
Don't act
like I'm in this alone.

37:43.548 --> 37:44.745
Don't act like you don't know

37:44.755 --> 37:48.703
what affection from a woman
feels like.

37:48.713 --> 37:51.412
I am not proud of it,
but I own it.

37:51.422 --> 37:52.870
Okay, this is ridiculous.

37:52.880 --> 37:55.912
When Mary Jane kicked you out
when you broke up,

37:55.922 --> 37:58.703
who was rubbing your back,
letting you crash on my couch

37:58.713 --> 38:00.703
until you figured out
your next move?

38:00.713 --> 38:03.496
When you were sick,
who was getting soup for you?

38:03.506 --> 38:05.579
And when all of this stuff
with Mary Jane was going on,

38:05.589 --> 38:07.870
who told you about the sperm?

38:07.880 --> 38:09.829
And who took care of your dog
all the damn time

38:09.839 --> 38:11.703
when you were flying
out of town?

38:11.713 --> 38:13.329
I mean, hell,
look who is cooking

38:13.339 --> 38:14.912
and cleaning for you now.

38:14.922 --> 38:17.454
And who gave you 50 grand
for your company?

38:17.464 --> 38:20.412
That was an investment, Lisa,
and you know it was.

38:20.422 --> 38:24.829
No. That was a woman in love
with you giving you money.

38:24.839 --> 38:27.329
But it was easier
for you to not believe it,

38:27.339 --> 38:28.412
because it benefitted you.

38:28.422 --> 38:30.287
That was an investment.

38:30.297 --> 38:31.538
You were paid back.

38:31.548 --> 38:32.787
We have paperwork.

38:32.797 --> 38:34.329
That's all it was?

38:34.339 --> 38:35.703
Does Mary Jane know about it?

38:37.713 --> 38:39.246
You didn't tell M.J.
about the money

38:39.256 --> 38:40.703
or the other stuff,

38:40.713 --> 38:43.538
because you feel
just as guilty as I do.

